 Syntax:  .search <search_string>
          .search email <search_string>

Results:  Searches all message boards for a particular word or character
          string. <search_string> is the string you are searching for.
          If you give the word "email" first, it'll search your mailfile
          for the search string.

Example:  To look for my name in all the boards, I type: .search cygnus
